    # fd "Normally, I'd invite you to come back to my place and we could hang out and maybe mess around a little..."
    fd "通常的话，我会邀请你回我住处，我们可以一起待着，说不定还能调情一下……"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:200
translate chinese brandi8kiss_6a600759:

    # fd "But I'm actually really busy after this. I have to write blog posts and make clips for YouTube and all of that."
    fd "但我其实接下来很忙。我得写博客文章，还要为YouTube剪辑视频之类的。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:201
translate chinese brandi8kiss_a9cb880b:

    # fd "And I'm kinda enjoying having our relationship progress a little bit every time on the stream. Next date, we'll take things a little further."
    fd "而且我挺享受这种每次直播时，我们的关系都能稍微进展一点的感觉。 下次约会，我们可以更进一步。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:202
translate chinese brandi8kiss_a2a6fb65:

    # pc "What do you mean?"
    pc "你什么意思？"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:203
translate chinese brandi8kiss_c6376995:

    # fd "I'm not sure yet. We'll just have to see when it happens. Hopefully soon."
    fd "我还不确定。到时候自然会知道。希望很快就能实现。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:206
translate chinese brandi8kiss_2e47b5f8:

    # "She leans in and we kiss again, lingering for a while, enjoying the moment."
    "她凑近我，我们再次接吻，久久不愿分开，尽情享受这一刻。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:207
translate chinese brandi8kiss_56324afa:

    # "Her hand touches my chest, rubbing, obviously wanting more than just kissing."
    "她的手抚上我的胸膛，轻轻摩挲，显然不满足于仅仅接吻。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:210
translate chinese brandi8kiss_57ca3c84:

    # "But she pulls away once again."
    "但她又一次退开了。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:211
translate chinese brandi8kiss_60ae11f7:

    # fd "Oh man. I could get addicted to that."
    fd "天啊。我可能会对这种感觉上瘾。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:212
translate chinese brandi8kiss_7d47f573:

    # fd "I don't want to stop, but I want to take it a little slow. One step at a time."
    fd "我不想停下来，但想慢慢来。一步一个脚印。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:213
translate chinese brandi8kiss_6f6de308:

    # fd "Thanks again for coming out with me. I really have to go though."
    fd "再次感谢你陪我出来。不过我真的得走了。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:214
translate chinese brandi8kiss_3898fbf5:

    # pc "Okay, no problem. I'm looking forward to seeing you again."
    pc "好的，没问题。期待下次再见。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:215
translate chinese brandi8kiss_d026f778:

    # fd "Oh me too. Bye, [pcname]."
    fd "哦，我也是。再见，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:218
translate chinese brandi8kiss_f2567900:

    # "She pays for the meal and we walk out together, then get in our separate cars and drive away."
    "她结了账，我们一起走出餐厅，随后各自上车驶离。"

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:219
translate chinese brandi8kiss_7bfa1389:

    # "Brandi is fun as always. I really am looking forward to seeing her again."
    "布兰迪一如既往地有趣。我真的很期待再见到她。"

